yTime":"2019-04-01T18:19:13.000Z","msg":"異度空間<br />\n<br />\n依套戲令到我有抑鬱"},{"pid":"8bbeb88d3f9f7ae49af658b5ca19a8307e1735c2","tid":1087944,"uid":78460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T18:30:58.000Z","msg":"大隻佬"},{"pid":"3ec64bd567707643a4c913ffe0e6131600486e5c","tid":1087944,"uid":176010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T18:34:36.000Z","msg":"夜勤病棟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaedde4d8320b81d745b5cb9dedd1fe1b163bb14","tid":1087944,"uid":213945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T18:37:44.000Z","msg":"教育電視有集講農藥，特別話係菜心花芯易積聚<br />\n一直去到依加都唔食花芯"},{"pid":"596c7fc8886085761b4cfaa79c51d417f3ccabd7","tid":1087944,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T18:39:10.000Z","msg":"一：幼稚園俾兩個成日恰我嘅同學搶玩具，跟住我發脾氣扔粒積木落地，個老師屌𨳊我，我就伏喺張枱度喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二：都係幼稚園，平日我好似有過度活躍症咁成日發癲，然後有一次要行出去畫畫，老師叫我哋要手拖手行出去，個女同學話我太癲，唔敢拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c2221bbff025fba71d3e560ecdaa6dc295c665","tid":1087944,"uid":1411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"49c1f53270ef2c318f9afcbc59f38dae833e2678","tid":1087944,"uid":166931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T16:19:34.000Z","msg":"記得細個睇電視 有個節目係用真人演繹啲鬼故出嚟<br />\n有一集係有個男人入lift 之後架lift慢慢好多血湧出來<br />\n然後個男人開始七孔流血 <br />\n睇完嗰集之後我每次答lift都好驚 驚到喊<br />\n都維持都好耐下 <br />\n事格二幾年都仲記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T18:48:29.000Z","msg":"奇幻潮 一筒歸西果集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf1dbad8929a1d76e9437a1d5d4d71177b4b3d3b","tid":1087944,"uid":1411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e06ed698a791d9e9ae6b60152811a6456c983a65","tid":1087944,"uid":61363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:06:33.000Z","msg":"奇幻潮 七色天晶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T18:50:33.000Z","msg":"記得細個睇完真係發惡夢見到個人比竹插穿咁行過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b500f22a7610b4c9d0a0b035b6292bb8ae3b1e","tid":1087944,"uid":62858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T19:28:24.000Z","msg":"沉默之丘 廁所入邊有隻野爬出黎個段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8097d8a0d5cc9c0216ba746e2b39bde80054a8b7","tid":1087944,"uid":245803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c69d7c9c8f5a29302c5e8684ca581b5ec9809abc","tid":1087944,"uid":196013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e15569292dc88c2885fcb875ace67bfd1f156b4","tid":1087944,"uid":245803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T16:25:48.000Z","msg":"法證先鋒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:03:16.000Z","msg":"法證先鋒3啲小丑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T02:56:21.000Z","msg":"宜家大個睇重播都仲係好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e73bf1aad28d6916e3c13d7f63c2bd129a36855","tid":1087944,"uid":164928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T03:33:51.000Z","msg":"細個果陣有一次陪老母返大陸，<br />\n坐親戚部車上汕頭定唔知汕尾。<br />\n點知好死唔死中途壞車，<br />\n咪迫住係個唔知咩地方嘅修車場整車，<br />\n點知佢話你部車一時三刻整唔好，<br />\n咁咪叫另一個親戚渣車嚟接囉。<br />\n幾條友就屈係人地個車場到等。<br />\n（上面全部廢話，重點係下面）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由朝早等到傍晚整來都相安無事，<br />\n突然有三個男人渣住開山刀沖入嚟，<br />\n本身以為係打劫，<br />\n點不知果三個男人同車場老闆鬧交，<br />\n話老闆搶走隔離車場生意之類，<br />\n我哋啲局外人梗係走埋一二角啦，<br />\n車場都有三個人，<br />\n不過係老闆自己同老婆同個幾歲嘅女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇幾耐就講唔掂數，<br />\n有個渣刀嘅行去老闆個老婆到，<br />\n個老婆已經驚到攬實個女，<br />\n渣刀條友攞把刀嘅刀側拍左個靚妹塊臉幾下，<br />\n嚇到老婆同個女尖叫，<br />\n咁老闆梗係反抗啦，<br />\n但奈何雙拳難敵四手，更何況係三刀？<br />\n係開片果一刻老母同親戚抱住我走，<br />\n但當時連毛都未生嘅我回頭一望，<br />\n一片腥風血雨，老闆變左做楊過<br />\n跌係地上不停捱刀. . . . . .<br />\n而件事之後變成點已經唔知道了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自此我就冇再返過大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae51c886ab606ab34d923a13dd4ee92f31de8b7","tid":1087944,"uid":141072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T03:41:08.000Z","msg":"阿哥同家姐亂倫<br />\n<br />\n兩次親眼見到人從廿幾樓跳樓<br />\n<br />\n被童黨掉落排污渠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65696594cc17cc3612d858b9d8563feb292a55b","tid":1087944,"uid":166931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93c2221bbff025fba71d3e560ecdaa6dc295c665","tid":1087944,"uid":1411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"49c1f53270ef2c318f9afcbc59f38dae833e2678","tid":1087944,"uid":166931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T16:19:34.000Z","msg":"記得細個睇電視 有個節目係用真人演繹啲鬼故出嚟<br />\n有一集係有個男人入lift 之後架lift慢慢好多血湧出來<br />\n然後個男人開始七孔流血 <br />\n睇完嗰集之後我每次答lift都好驚 驚到喊<br />\n都維持都好耐下 <br />\n事格二幾年都仲記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T18:48:29.000Z","msg":"奇幻潮 一筒歸西果集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:02:12.000Z","msg":"好似唔係 我記得細個睇嗰陣 架電梯仲會越嚟越窄"}]}